{"tid":1788703,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"芬蘭向全世界免費開放在線AI速成班","createTime":"2019-12-19T01:30:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-12T01:32:40.000Z","uid":335391,"like":97,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"fcaf026a1a95e6413025b624d0bb078c858719d6","tid":1788703,"uid":335391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T01:30:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.theverge.com/2019/12/18/21027840/online-course-basics-of-ai-finland-free-elements\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theverge.com%2F2019%2F12%2F18%2F21027840%2Fonline-course-basics-of-ai-finland-free-elements&d=CSzjam5d59%2B0TSQi2Kgm6gogPkW5zMkxdNnzPoGklno%3D&h=c380457c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.theverge.com/2019/12/18/21027840/online-course-basics-of-ai-finland-free-elements</a><br />\n去年，芬蘭推出了一個免費的人工智能(AI)在線在線速成班，目的是教育其公民有關新技術的知識。現在，作為送給全世界的聖誕節禮物，這個歐洲國家正在提供為期六週的節目，任何人都可以參加<br />\n<br />\n嚴格來說，這是送給歐盟的禮物。芬蘭將在年底放棄歐盟輪值主席國的資格，並決定將其課程翻譯成每種歐盟語言，作為對公民的禮物。但是，關於誰可以參加此課程沒有任何地域限制，因此這確實對全世界都有利。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4DUgxFP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4DUgxFP.png&h=276a6ed4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n當然，該課程在芬蘭得到了證明，北歐國家的550萬公民中有1％以上簽了名。該課程名為AI元素，目前提供英語，瑞典語，愛沙尼亞語，芬蘭語和德語版本。<br />\n...<br />\n芬蘭政府表示，其最初設計該課程的目的是使其公民在人工智能方面具有優勢。芬蘭一直在技術和教育上力所能及，因此將兩者結合起來似乎是明智的。技術諮詢公司Reaktor的Megan Schaible幫助設計了該課程，他說的動機是&ldquo;證明AI不應交由少數精英編碼人員掌握。&rdquo;"},{"pid":"e29741715042b1148e73b2374a0665e85eadb594","tid":1788703,"uid":263197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T03:46:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d60aa095228e137b1008739d28ea8a92dded2b92","tid":1788703,"uid":222614,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"repl